---
title: Haloumi & Dukkah Couscous with Roasted Veggies & Lemon Yoghurt Drizzle
description: Taste the rainbow for dinner tonight with an assortment of colourful roasted veggies and a scattering of sweet currants, all stirred through
fluffy, filling couscous. Topped off with golden haloumi and nutty dukkah, this robust bowl packs a punch in all the right ways.
